{"id": "e2f6376ada2ed1326ae949ae483811afb8b2cd073695755511bee5fe15722888", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:0", "text": "RenderMan for Maya can substitute a number of predefined tokens in string parameters. They can be used for animated texture sequences, referencing specific storage locations, etc."}
{"id": "d2089be672953d1136faa84079af1b6f3967fed8932dabffba3032d30e3c0618", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:1", "text": "Token"}
{"id": "1f5d64b92820f8238635b90ae69a38c12661a7b03c6d0d7f689711f12af7b7f9", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:2", "text": "Meaning"}
{"id": "dcbffe8bd88cf843b1717f9a0e2d51f7a83fcc028e7acdeb56aa35e6a7887067", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:3", "text": "<scene>"}
{"id": "e3fe736a010f44035ac3928c3776cc94203dc8c7b48bf447cf931bb527eefb0a", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:4", "text": "Scene name"}
{"id": "2cfeceb94005e12c68cd0c5b733ded0c108685fe9dfa25d6ff089aa8685b4819", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:5", "text": "<layer>"}
{"id": "21cfb523986c71466b335c2143a8e6ab7f338bcae5b25999dc5d6420c7d3d4fc", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:6", "text": "Maya Render Layer name"}
{"id": "5989379f18ac176d4e8da694773989008ac135c1a0264502e66d35d09218ebdb", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:7", "text": "<camera>"}
{"id": "85b87a41e007930befb761904ca1b1823d28d1b13dc354bd28ce5f5dfe1ca73f", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:8", "text": "Render camera name"}
{"id": "3b6875920a36b444a9a8c7196087ec60fb5488744bb2234403227bf3bfa0e48b", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:9", "text": "<aov>"}
{"id": "2fdf625e5193d4be2eca3c3c570b8152d3f9a25f272daacd34c43b9cff9e59e6", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:10", "text": "AOV or LPE name"}
{"id": "eb89d1bb8e9344cd48b219292e5d9b8af640bb9320a42753283b1bf1c332163d", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:11", "text": "<aovdir>"}
{"id": "9ec4eaa3caab952971edca8f37f8ac0087fb82ecf9daa3678eb79cf3dbdb9c4d", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:12", "text": "This will write AOVs to named sub-directories"}
{"id": "a1b0641066c89bd60eb5674c47cbdd7bc63c9abab46316a71f8ab0cedd09bde7", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:13", "text": "<f4>"}
{"id": "5f64fa5245c20d58e229f2e57abfea063b43f56b0a81d12adddd0b47b3913f02", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:14", "text": "Frame padding, 4 in this case, can be omitted for no padding or use lower numbers"}
{"id": "3d86ebe97130186c673df02b52d2f6fec0c676ae548cb5a92ebcbd87b9ba8e06", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:15", "text": "<ext>"}
{"id": "26eafba06a73a8324431bc52a96223f68d91bcf332ae067a5b502e24a31565de", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:16", "text": "File type extension"}
{"id": "8d81c90dd65238128850c57c58a3c0d015228359c279a7b2dce19fecb1b1fc45", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:17", "text": "<ws>"}
{"id": "8e13310e8a3cc2bd07897058ebf390b631186f6ca79600b2860a7f82cbf51880", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:18", "text": "Maya's current workspace, the file path in your project"}
{"id": "644675e584d12c440b4fba83b25ede56ef7d13d0a0999d1b19a7899d53cd80b2", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:19", "text": "<version>"}
{"id": "5807a9abadc53e2486c8c7dbbf03fa2891cfba55ff23f643936fa2a09ce4eff8", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:20", "text": "Inserts the version number specified above"}
{"id": "ccb4e57cf6752637e4ecdca2068aea359ad13ecee71dad0adaa66ad50168f5d3", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:21", "text": "<take>"}
{"id": "f435309cbcf460f88f8bd517f04611fb0ac5b1bc56c55fdb0efe436593c12742", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:22", "text": "Inserts the take number specified above"}
{"id": "b2fae905cd7d2c75a03e83b51fe0544a300dbabcb343761ce224554cb3f54d68", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:23", "text": "<date>"}
{"id": "88d4758c212fc3ed328a188df55e2c413f30ac6afa6aa37567310eeda7643276", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:24", "text": "Current date"}
{"id": "49c5d043bfa0858d6eab646d2682962a7f267a88d3656c1d4bf711601c23d5b4", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:25", "text": "<assetlib>"}
{"id": "327bc4f4194b5a9b42387dcf4d8604e66f2d039e8208e9f9007898ebb98c6b9a", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:26", "text": "Path to the standard RenderMan Asset Library"}
{"id": "d5a7c9c99679aea62d365254dcdbe63bb27f37c775cdb2ad6af8241ce201731b", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:27", "text": "<file>"}
{"id": "2513a7c270f933d372bc421065242847590dc72de0a51e5166d3aef8b06bef9e", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:28", "text": "Scene file name"}
{"id": "44e11b133d51cc80851cf1e7c267e8226f210bfa7a827bb164501980ee9279b4", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:29", "text": "<frame>"}
{"id": "197de756ca88eaee6e597fc9c8f7dda7f2fb39241e48eebb085dba13c8b32cbb", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:30", "text": "Decimal frame number"}
{"id": "b930457b07ef98dd404b1e87bc0da7ee298f3d8207a8d9f8067c212cd94815e4", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:31", "text": "<jobid>"}
{"id": "f93d3d62510100424b0f71d5747daa412fbaaeaaf7e352620eac773c967cc3b3", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:32", "text": "Unique job identifier"}
{"id": "339febdaa6146c3e93b988f142113b3364cc3b8814ff69b9841ba9e9c6ce6cf8", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:33", "text": "<shape>"}
{"id": "725503a9ad3bfea198cc651de5b9f356fc78990541311175c92191c50bc4fd62", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:34", "text": "Short shape name (all instances have the same shape name)"}
{"id": "b0c241ea36b2a132cdc4138fe057282413d84e43cd007e13320bb84f7837846a", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:35", "text": "<shapepath>"}
{"id": "a89505d37b4bb8be4536ad7f7ac3664e41b5d72429323aa6ac6dd6d81def0fe8", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:36", "text": "Long shape name (all instances have unique"}
{"id": "bd5f4dc6f7ce9d2a16ad837ce1539b77386b1f0d035af0c0174aeafb9ea9f2b5", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:37", "text": "shapepath names)"}
{"id": "26c0d874961ff4a7350ffee0208d9c8bc7ac4d4f3b8102184180b6f08aca2778", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:38", "text": "<time>"}
{"id": "06dafda7802b6be989948770b31c934bf86812482333e3d84d57855a7b6cd17e", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:39", "text": "Current time"}
{"id": "a8f1a055220aaea9983d281c6688849632cfc5c8b02d2dc8215bafbdc5deec72", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:40", "text": "<udim>"}
{"id": "cbfa2b21da8dc918dc48b7b29ab8d3d3f9c7c747424f440088a4262caa58ad68", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:41", "text": "UDIM identifier (only substituted at render time)"}
{"id": "23e52b53a1ae913539d2d4aa4f666183ec29b6493e95edb84ef0e13c21174a8c", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:42", "text": "<imagedir>"}
{"id": "2ef6b3c8d3668f81b3d21fa4421346b77b0513bc5ad423df9beb668081b3fb88", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:43", "text": "This contains the full image output directory"}
{"id": "d4986077e9e4c8d5ea617a7959502874e9d00e37ab31cb63c2e865e56d4253a7", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:44", "text": "_MAPID_"}
{"id": "4741a344e453a6b022f197541bf1e1768557ae39623cc2d024e051efe2a07bf6", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:45", "text": "Generic texture atlas identifier"}
{"id": "07aea15d2ac29476ea1339c09cb8c692133abc174ae7691c870e1c75d17968ff", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:46", "text": "(only substituted at render time)"}
{"id": "1124ecc667c5f22e3a6d6275c661d4c5f6fe66bc74ccc278a00ea0cccd8d3a5b", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:47", "text": "Environment Variables"}
{"id": "5f41a5e8acfc55273076657233cea4703dc5f08eaeb38f4435a86de08aa6a4db", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:48", "text": "Environment variables must start with the $ sign and only use capitals, numbers and \"_\" characters:"}
{"id": "441243aaafd8ce5af44a704cd96096c39f5d718d5de2907f75e6d5f29f6778cb", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:49", "text": ": returns the path to the txmake utility."}
{"id": "869f3db27b34a60c1b4b9924ca4d4e33523d576a1d7ecbb71524f46f9a95fbbd", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:50", "text": "Curly braces can also be used for composition:"}
{"id": "b44865ad18d518a871240a537577d1bcbb4e6656c3f6ef2c43b22526461cd00b", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:51", "text": "Retrieving attribute values"}
{"id": "854f54382a79042546e26661a5f3c435bfcb240613370506b56c4b2ecee14123", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:52", "text": "RfM does not support TCL expression anymore but allows for attribute evaluation:"}
{"id": "0dcea249c73373ee66bd7e314db5e8af7b60b6d152ace12f824057d75558efb0", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:53", "text": "returns the value of the 'time' attribute on the shape node ('shape' as opposed to the 'transform' node)."}
{"id": "9095786a4b2b43b501872734673b7090cc3177e71ea73979d00274be76e6337f", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:54", "text": "It is also possible to format numerical attribute values by specifying a formatting string:"}
{"id": "b3622eb71b3eee34d77cb75dd9f317e44e31cab06ee22c161e142b0bbe5f05a3", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:55", "text": ": if time's value is"}
{"id": "6e0e9dbed443b5dedfb8fa136fc0cfe92b3facfa576a2776de3dda46dc99b292", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:56", "text": ", this will return"}
{"id": "5fa35241ae057800d1beb2debec08fa6499c9c7b47a3adf3aa0cf4fcababfc59", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:58", "text": "This is using"}
{"id": "bad818910bb7ef00f6b8afb44b1232db292a19f8070d8bdcf5e89c1193e9a21c", "item_id": "a1374ebe46:59", "text": "python's standard format specifiers"}
